<title>Protest isn&#39;t civil</title>
<content type="html" xml:lang="en">&lt;p&gt;Stallman Sez: &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.commondreams.org/views/2018/06/28/protest-isnt-civil&#34;&gt;Protest Isnâ€™t Civil.&lt;/a&gt; Indeed, protest against unjust rule cannot be effective if it accepts the limits imposed by unjust rule.   &lt;/p&gt;</content>
