<title>Deportation prison deals</title>
<content type="html" xml:lang="en">&lt;p&gt;Stallman Sez: &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; Many US cities and counties &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.nytimes.com/2018/06/28/us/migrant-shelters-ice-contracts-counties.html&#34;&gt;have cancelled deals&lt;/a&gt; with the deportation thugs to hold their prisoners.   &lt;/p&gt;</content>
