<title>Supreme court appointments</title>
<content type="html" xml:lang="en">&lt;p&gt;Stallman Sez: &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; Senator McConnell said that blocking the appointment of a supreme court justice for a whole year until the 2016 election was not mere partisanship &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.commondreams.org/news/2018/06/27/midtermsbeforescotus-takes-democrats-told-stiffen-their-spines&#34;&gt;but a civic duty&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; Naturally this time he intends to rush the process of replacing Kennedy.   &lt;/p&gt;</content>
<category term="stallman"/>
<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://localhost:8000/post/01CHH9DC00JG4FHTBBRFDAQK7S.html"/>
