<id>http://localhost:8000/post/01CHH9DC00HHMTWMJK5DTFGGT1.html</id>
<published>2018-07-04T00:00:00.000Z</published>
<updated>2018-07-04T00:00:00.000Z</updated>
<title>Britain: Homeless fined or jailed</title>
<content type="html" xml:lang="en">&lt;p&gt;Stallman Sez: &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Many &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.theguardian.com/society/2018/may/20/homeless-people-fined-imprisoned-pspo-england-wales&#34;&gt;towns in Britain repress homeless beggars&lt;/a&gt;, fining them or jailing them for begging.  It almost resembles the US.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;If you don&#39;t want people to beg, don&#39;t make them destitute!&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  </content>
<category term="stallman"/>
<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://localhost:8000/post/01CHH9DC00HHMTWMJK5DTFGGT1.html"/>
</entry>
