<title>Union membership</title>
<content type="html" xml:lang="en">&lt;p&gt;Stallman Sez: &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; Young American workers are &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.theguardian.com/world/2018/jun/29/can-millennials-save-unions-in-america&#34;&gt;joining and organizing unions&lt;/a&gt;, reinvigorating them.   &lt;/p&gt;</content>
