<published>2018-07-04T00:00:00.000Z</published>
<updated>2018-07-04T00:00:00.000Z</updated>
<title>Nature disappearing</title>
<content type="html" xml:lang="en">&lt;p&gt;Stallman Sez: &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; George Monbiot says that &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2018/jun/29/natural-world-disappearing-save-it&#34;&gt;nature is disappearing&lt;/a&gt; in front of relentless human alteration of ecosystems: one after another, species that used to be abundant have become rare or disappeared entirely where he lives.   &lt;/p&gt;</content>
<category term="stallman"/>
<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://localhost:8000/post/01CHH9DC00ER6M9C12NAPNEE9X.html"/>
</entry>
