<id>http://localhost:8000/post/01CHH9DC00EAAHQJVTSK59V07K.html</id>
<published>2018-07-04T00:00:00.000Z</published>
<updated>2018-07-04T00:00:00.000Z</updated>
<title>Seaweed in place of plastic</title>
<content type="html" xml:lang="en">&lt;p&gt;Stallman Sez: &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; Indonesia could &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.theguardian.com/environment/blog/2018/jun/27/could-seaweed-solve-indonesias-plastic-crisis&#34;&gt;use seaweed to replace plastic&lt;/a&gt; for food packaging, ten years from now. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; But it will require government pressure to stop using plastic.   &lt;/p&gt;</content>
<category term="stallman"/>
<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://localhost:8000/post/01CHH9DC00EAAHQJVTSK59V07K.html"/>
</entry>
<entry>
<id>http://localhost:8000/post/01CHH9DC00DBVXP0S77K46A1TS.html</id>
<published>2018-07-04T00:00:00.000Z</published>
<updated>2018-07-04T00:00:00.000Z</updated>
<title>Farm bill blocked</title>
<content type="html" xml:lang="en">&lt;p&gt;Stallman Sez: &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The disastrous &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2018/may/18/farm-bill-paul-ryan-food-stamps-house-freedom-caucus&#34;&gt;Republican farm bill was blocked&lt;/a&gt; because some Republicans demand more repression of immigrants.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;We can&#39;t expect this to save us permanently from the &lt;a href=&#34;https://stallman.org/archives/2012-may-aug.html#08_July_2012_(House_Farm_Bill)&#34;&gt;nasty&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://stallman.org/archives/2018-mar-jun.html#25_June_2018_(Farm_bill_and_the_environment)&#34;&gt;provisions&lt;/a&gt; of the farm bill.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  </content>
<category term="stallman"/>
<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://localhost:8000/post/01CHH9DC00DBVXP0S77K46A1TS.html"/>
</entry>
<entry>
<id>http://localhost:8000/post/01CHH9DC00CGGZMCW8N0KAFVYQ.html</id>
<published>2018-07-04T00:00:00.000Z</published>
<updated>2018-07-04T00:00:00.000Z</updated>
<title>Database law in California</title>
<content type="html" xml:lang="en">&lt;p&gt;Stallman Sez: &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; California has adopted a &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2018/jun/28/california-privacy-bill-data-harvesting&#34;&gt;stricter-than-usual law&lt;/a&gt; to regulate commercial databases. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; It will probably do some good, but if it does what the article suggests, it won&#39;t stop the recordings made from cameras and microphones in the street and in buses, or real-time face recognition on their images, and I doubt it will do much good regarding phone company tracking of phone calls, messages and locations.   &lt;/p&gt;</content>
<category term="stallman"/>
<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://localhost:8000/post/01CHH9DC00CGGZMCW8N0KAFVYQ.html"/>
</entry>
<entry>
<id>http://localhost:8000/post/01CHH9DC00C0JAQ6RBYNSRPK0N.html</id>
<published>2018-07-04T00:00:00.000Z</published>
<updated>2018-07-04T00:00:00.000Z</updated>
<title>Dark patterns</title>
<content type="html" xml:lang="en">&lt;p&gt;Stallman Sez: &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; A report surveys how companies including Facebook, Google and Microsoft design systems to &lt;a href=&#34;https://edri.org/ncc-report-on-dark-patterns/&#34;&gt;hamper users from exercizing their rights&lt;/a&gt;.   &lt;/p&gt;</content>
<category term="stallman"/>
<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://localhost:8000/post/01CHH9DC00C0JAQ6RBYNSRPK0N.html"/>
</entry>
<entry>
<id>http://localhost:8000/post/01CHH9DC00C08GBFXDM4SPVM2Q.html</id>
<published>2018-07-04T00:00:00.000Z</published>
<updated>2018-07-04T00:00:00.000Z</updated>
<title>Rendition in the UK</title>
<content type="html" xml:lang="en">&lt;p&gt;Stallman Sez: &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2018/jun/28/uks-role-in-rendition-and-torture-of-terrorism-suspects-key-findings&#34;&gt;UK law was designed&lt;/a&gt; to allow spy agencies to kidnap people and hand them over to dictators to be tortured. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; Successive governments have &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2018/jun/28/uk-risk-future-human-rights-abuses-isc-reports&#34;&gt;covered up the details&lt;/a&gt; to protect the agents involved and the ministers who gave them orders. As a result, similar things could easily happen again.   &lt;/p&gt;</content>
<category term="stallman"/>
<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://localhost:8000/post/01CHH9DC00C08GBFXDM4SPVM2Q.html"/>
</entry>
