<published>2018-07-04T00:00:00.000Z</published>
<updated>2018-07-04T00:00:00.000Z</updated>
<title>Intervening for Palestinians</title>
<content type="html" xml:lang="en">&lt;p&gt;Stallman Sez: &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &amp;quot;As Israelis, we call on the world to &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2018/jun/29/israelis-call-world-intervene-behalf-palestinians&#34;&gt;intervene on behalf of Palestinians&lt;/a&gt;.&amp;quot;   &lt;/p&gt;</content>
<category term="stallman"/>
<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://localhost:8000/post/01CHH9DC008GFWBHNB6QKJ77HM.html"/>
</entry>
<entry>
<id>http://localhost:8000/post/01CHH9DC008D0GE2MXEJRZ0D0B.html</id>
<published>2018-07-04T00:00:00.000Z</published>
<updated>2018-07-04T00:00:00.000Z</updated>
<title>Carbon emissions tax</title>
<content type="html" xml:lang="en">&lt;p&gt;Stallman Sez: &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; Republicans representing oil companies are proposing a carbon emissions tax.  However, at the the &lt;a href=&#34;https://truthout.org/articles/oil-companies-and-lobbyists-say-theyre-ready-to-solve-climate-change-check-the-fine-print/&#34;&gt;cost of big concessions&lt;/a&gt;.   &lt;/p&gt;</content>
<category term="stallman"/>
<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://localhost:8000/post/01CHH9DC008D0GE2MXEJRZ0D0B.html"/>
</entry>
<entry>
<id>http://localhost:8000/post/01CHH9DC007MX2CGSJSRX56TG9.html</id>
<published>2018-07-04T00:00:00.000Z</published>
<updated>2018-07-04T00:00:00.000Z</updated>
<title>LocationSmart phone tracking</title>
<content type="html" xml:lang="en">&lt;p&gt;Stallman Sez: &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The LocationSmart web site enabled anyone to roughly  &lt;a href=&#34;https://krebsonsecurity.com/2018/05/tracking-firm-locationsmart-leaked-location-data-for-customers-of-all-major-u-s-mobile-carriers-in-real-time-via-its-web-site/&#34;&gt;track the position of any mobile phone&lt;/a&gt;, due to completely missing security.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;However, anyone willing to commit a crime can get the same data through &lt;a href=&#34;https://stallman.org/archives/2012-sep-dec.html#17_December_2012_(Location_privacy_bill)&#34;&gt;the bad security of the SS7 protocol&lt;/a&gt; through which one phone network talks with another phone network.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Even worse, the data is easily available the government.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;This is one reason I refuse to carry a mobile phone. The other is that &lt;a href=&#34;https://gnu.org/malware/malware-mobiles.html&#34;&gt;it can be modified through a back door&lt;/a&gt; to listen and transmit all conversations in its vicinity.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  </content>
<category term="stallman"/>
<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://localhost:8000/post/01CHH9DC007MX2CGSJSRX56TG9.html"/>
</entry>
<entry>
<id>http://localhost:8000/post/01CHH9DC0079Z9XV0CYEBW0MD5.html</id>
<published>2018-07-04T00:00:00.000Z</published>
<updated>2018-07-04T00:00:00.000Z</updated>
<title>Amazon warehouse like prison</title>
<content type="html" xml:lang="en">&lt;p&gt;Stallman Sez: &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Working in an Amazon warehouse is like being in prison &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.businessinsider.com/amazon-warehouse-like-prison-where-workers-used-pee-bottle-2018-4?r=UK&amp;amp;IR=T&#34;&gt;with a sentence of hard and hurried labor&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;The workers don&#39;t have breaks even enough to go to the toilet.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  </content>
<category term="stallman"/>
<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://localhost:8000/post/01CHH9DC0079Z9XV0CYEBW0MD5.html"/>
</entry>
<entry>
<id>http://localhost:8000/post/01CHH9DC006XAJQ9YS0VFDFG2P.html</id>
<published>2018-07-04T00:00:00.000Z</published>
<updated>2018-07-04T00:00:00.000Z</updated>
<title>Prisoners and elections</title>
<content type="html" xml:lang="en">&lt;p&gt;Stallman Sez: &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; The number of prisoners in the US is so high that it &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.commondreams.org/newswire/2018/06/28/new-report-examines-business-mass-incarceration-damage-it-does-democracy&#34;&gt;directly alters elections&lt;/a&gt;. Groups that suffer bigotry are imprisoned unfairly more than others, even after committing similar crimes, and that costs them voting strength.  Moreover, prisons placed in right-wing areas make their votes count extra.   &lt;/p&gt;</content>
<category term="stallman"/>
<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://localhost:8000/post/01CHH9DC006XAJQ9YS0VFDFG2P.html"/>
</entry>
<entry>
<id>http://localhost:8000/post/01CHH9DC006TTPSMQV4BPG8PB5.html</id>
<published>2018-07-04T00:00:00.000Z</published>
<updated>2018-07-04T00:00:00.000Z</updated>
<title>Protesting family imprisonment</title>
<content type="html" xml:lang="en">&lt;p&gt;Stallman Sez: &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2018/jun/28/us-immigration-protest-trump-washington-senate&#34;&gt;600 protesters held a sit-in&lt;/a&gt; in a US Senate office building, demanding an end to imprisonment of refugee families. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; I think that the &lt;a href=&#34;https://stallman.org/glossary.html#bully&#34;&gt;bully&lt;/a&gt; will use this as an excuse to increase repression. He has no desire for civil peace, any more than international peace.   &lt;/p&gt;</content>
<category term="stallman"/>
<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://localhost:8000/post/01CHH9DC006TTPSMQV4BPG8PB5.html"/>
</entry>
